Read request
  Which node to choose? https://www.datastax.com/dev/blog/dynamic-snitching-in-cassandra-past-present-and-future
    1. dynamic_snitch_update_interval_in_ms : how long to require nodes information
    2. dynamic_snitch_reset_interval_in_ms : how long to let other nodes to have a fair chance
    3. dynamic_snitch_badness_threshold : how bad a node performance compare to others could trigger the node switch
  Which types of read request? https://docs.datastax.com/en/dse/5.1/dse-arch/datastax_enterprise/dbInternals/dbIntClientRequestsRead.html#dbIntClientRequestsRead

